Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.60,0:27:39.88,opch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an7}破碎的景色

Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.63,0:27:45.43,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}滲んでゆく風
